data.description: Open floor plan in this spacious home!  4 bedrooms!  1st floor bedroom and laundry rm.  Built in hutch & hardwood flooring in dining rm.  Hardwood floors under flooring in kitchen which offers an island & extra roomy cabinets!  Bay window in living rm.  Charming entry way with a foyer area offering 2 doors and porches.  Crown molding.  New gas/forced air furnace.  Central air. Updated plumbing Roomy enough for a nice sitting area.  Landing area upstairs also offers an open area that could be used for a sitting area.  Fenced in back yard with patio.  Garage.  Walk to downtown Williamston to events, restaurants, shopping & red cedar river.  Short drive to I 96 and Okemos/Lansing.
